Noteworthy points on alleged 🇪🇺#EU trade dependencies in a paper issued by @ECIPE 
⭐️trade data shows that except for only few products, 🇪🇺 does not have critical trade #dependencies on products & services imported from outside 🇪🇺. 
⭐️technology interdependencies between 🇪🇺 & none-🇪🇺countries are mutually beneficial.
⭐️trade & investment #interdependencies are unavoidable.
⭐️eliminating economic dependencies through restrictive regulations would negatively impact Member States’ economies.
⭐️to bolster its export, 🇪🇺 should initiate supply-oriented structural reforms & increase 🇪🇺 export’s competitiveness rather than limiting imports. 

🔗 https://t.co/ddtwHRwbGE
